<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1670702' id='t-1670702'>in a more intense and more focused way.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1674222' id='t-1674222'>The opposite of depression
is not happiness,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1677829' id='t-1677829'>but vitality,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1679163' id='t-1679163'>and these days, my life is vital,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1682142' id='t-1682142'>even on the days when I'm sad.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1684823' id='t-1684823'>I felt that funeral in my brain,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1687962' id='t-1687962'>and I sat next to the colossus
