<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1706841' id='t-1706841'>I think that while I hated being depressed</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1710678' id='t-1710678'>and would hate to be depressed again,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1713204' id='t-1713204'>I've found a way to love my depression.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1715894' id='t-1715894'>I love it because it has forced me
